&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Part-of / 独占 / 弱实体&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://peng-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/markdown-img/image-20220619210343391.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20220619210343391&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
